title: DDFP 295: Week 5 picks & MVP debate
itunes:title: DDFP 295: Week 5 picks & MVP debate
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Elliot Harrison to debate who has been the MVP of the 2014 NFL season so far. The guys also make their Week 5 predictions with NFL Network researcher Drew Christensen and try out some new treats from London.
